    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/8662432b87783474cb1c27467b68df46.poster.avif?t=1719818489\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/8662432b87783474cb1c27467b68df46.webm?t=1719818489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/8662432b87783474cb1c27467b68df46.mp4?t=1719818489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast-paced. Roguelike. Hack &amp; Slash. All-in-one package!</h2><strong>OVERKILL</strong> is where the supreme anger is released from your veins. Inspired by the fast-paced modern roguelikes and rhythmic games with roguelike elements, OVERKILL offers a setting where you constantly best monsters by evading their attacks via various dodge mechanics. You will smash your keyboard like you haven't before to <i>OVERKILL</i> your enemies with YOUR own <i>skill</i>, <i>strategy</i>, and <i>anger</i>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/d7447debe614eb67c8588d8eec6edc8f.poster.avif?t=1719818489\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/d7447debe614eb67c8588d8eec6edc8f.webm?t=1719818489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/d7447debe614eb67c8588d8eec6edc8f.mp4?t=1719818489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay &amp; Features</h2>The features specified below will take place in the release version of the game.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Various monsters with unique dodge mechanics.</li><li>Trinkets and items to create combat strategies.</li><li>Character abilities to combine and shape the gameplay.</li><li>A dark, medieval, fantastic atmosphere.</li><li>Random events throughout procedurally generated runs.</li><li>Optional story elements and character interactions.</li><li>Different difficulty settings for the ultimate challenge and achievements.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/aec0ceaf7045b0d916a0bda8fd854976.poster.avif?t=1719818489\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/aec0ceaf7045b0d916a0bda8fd854976.webm?t=1719818489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166360/extras/aec0ceaf7045b0d916a0bda8fd854976.mp4?t=1719818489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
